<i>adjective</i>: 큼직하다 [큼지카다], 큼지막하다 [큼지마카다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>큼직하다 [큼지카다]</dt><br>
<dd>biggish; rather big</dd><br>
<dd>꽤 크다.</dd><br>
<dd>Quite big.</dd><br>
<dt>큼지막하다 [큼지마카다]</dt><br>
<dd>biggish; rather big</dd><br>
<dd>꽤 큼직하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Quite big.</dd><br>
</li>
